IN RE the Personal Restraint of Eric Matthew HOPPER, Petitioner. No. 96274-0 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington, March 7, 2019.

ORDER

¶ 1 This case came before the Court on its March 7, 2019, En Banc Conference to consider the motion for discretionary review. A majority of the Court voted in favor of the following result:

¶ 2 Now, therefore, it is hereby

¶ 3 ORDERED:

¶ 4 That the motion for discretionary review is denied.

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, C.J. CHIEF JUSTICE
